author: ritchiem
msg: QPID-1535 : Update to FailoverMethodTest to address testNoFailover failures. Unable to locally reproduce failure so commiting to allow CI boxes to hammer result. As the broker shutdown can sometimes take a full 1s ensuring that we are notified in less time that 500ms is not going to work. Increased delay to 2s to ensure that we can confirm that we waited for less than that time when the connection is closed.
